{"tid":199660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[護眼]克羅地亞白鸛避寒回巢發現愛妻出軌 擊退情敵","createTime":"2017-04-13T11:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T02:26:57.000Z","uid":10319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83e8cc5abb871f2c41e4f6f1a64ac6190fc8d2df","tid":199660,"uid":10319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/58ef3c906db28c8b06ca0c31/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F58ef3c906db28c8b06ca0c31%2F&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=629af2d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/58ef3c906db28c8b06ca0c31/</a><br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞有對雙宿雙棲廿多年的白鸛，其中雄性白鸛每年都會到非洲過冬，雌性白鸛就因傷無法跟隨，每年春天雄性白鸛都會回來和愛妻團聚。今年牠遲了回來，卻出現了一些「意外」。<br />\n<br />\n多年來，克羅地亞都有個家傳戶曉的愛情故事。主角叫科雷派坦和馬萊娜，牠們的情緣由廿多年前開始，那年牠們在克羅地亞東部共築愛巢，一直不離不棄，哪怕每年冬天要飛過一萬三千公里到非洲避寒，牠們都形影不離。<br />\n<br />\n美好故事卻在十五年前出現變數，馬萊娜被人打傷翅膀，不能和科雷派坦一起到非洲。白鸛作為候鳥，科雷派坦不得不到非洲避寒，十五年來的冬天，牠們都天各一方。到三月底，科雷派坦都會回到愛巢，雖然去年因天氣問題遲了幾天到達，但最終都回來和馬萊娜團聚。<br />\n<br />\n今個春天，科雷派坦遲了兩個多星期才回來，怎料卻發現愛妻身邊多了一隻雄性白鸛。<br />\n<br />\n辛辛苦苦飛了萬多公里才發現愛妻有新「男伴」，科雷派坦「一怒之下」和「第三者」打起上來，結果已三十多歲的科雷派坦「寶刀未老」，順利「擊退」情敵，還將牠們誕下的蛋打碎，兩隻白鸛現已重過新生活。<br />\n<br />\n馬萊娜照顧者指：「他現在和她一起了，我想這故事會延續下去，他永遠不會遲。」至於科雷派坦的「情敵」下場如何，當地人都說不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8241efb158ebfb322d7b8111d6003cd656f7844","tid":199660,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:03:39.000Z","msg":"還將牠們誕下的蛋打碎"},{"pid":"de41cecd937c90b7d11d0f9041e442c4fd47019e","tid":199660,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"蛋都生埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5505c9920a6da2df4619757b0f64ecb9cdae52f","tid":199660,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:04:53.000Z","msg":"原來白鶴老婆係雞.....  呀睇錯 係白鸛 SORRY"},{"pid":"5b153af3df6b8536f298ecfb38dc4d35e567eebd","tid":199660,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"無聊新聞"},{"pid":"fd87e38a3218fc2ac0cf59c54e99f584380c8d83","tid":199660,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d307f61b2d823787ddf2b01515883705acffa49","tid":199660,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來白鶴老婆係雞.....  呀睇錯 係白鸛 SORRY</blockquote><br />\n好好笑，笑到停唔到"},{"pid":"2878e3ad06275c0a05d9dd11a5c8c7e4d1520af1","tid":199660,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e62407ba80ab2af1deee2d7af3bd716665546c","tid":199660,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛋都生埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmola mola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4481794f6613f4be900b77f667a434ee1f5e394c","tid":199660,"uid":10319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a7fee94d5d1803f1c11882feede511da2edf4f","tid":199660,"uid":10319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj